API.name: API
API.description:
The player API class
A signleton is made available in the global context under metaScoreAPI
HTML links that follow the following format are automatically parsed: {link text} An action can take arguments in the form of action=arg1,arg2,..
Multiple actions can be specified seperated by & Examples: PLAY PLAY EXTRACT PAUSE SEEL TO 500 SECONDS GOT TO PAGE 3 OF THE PERMANENTTEXT BLOCK SET THE READING INDEX TO 2 GOT TO PAGE 3 OF THE PERMANENTTEXT BLOCK AND SET THE READING INDEX TO 2 AND SEEK TO 500 SECONDS
